Essar Said to Offer Up to 80,000 Tons of Fuel Oil for January

-- B y   P r a t i s h   N a r a y a n a n
-- 
2011-12-07T08:28:38Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-12-07/essar-said-to-offer-up-to-80-000-tons-of-fuel-oil-for-january.html
Essar Oil Ltd. (ESOIL) , owner of India’s
second-largest non-state-owned refinery, offered to sell as much
as 80,000 metric tons of  fuel oil  for loading in January, said
two traders who declined to be identified because they aren’t
authorized to speak with the media.  Details of the offer are as follows:  To contact the reporter on this story:
